					<a href="http://en.gravatar.com/site/signup" class="gravatar"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=2a4f4f2259921a89fbb16f44034f395a&size=31&rating=R&d=identicon" alt="" /></a>					<div>
